quran[8{c,v,t}:
39,75,tum firshton ko dekho ge ke arsh ke gird ghaira bandhay hue hain ( aur ) apne perwar-digaar ki tareef ke sath tasbeeh kar rahay hain. aur un mein insaaf ke sath faislakiya jaye ga aur kaha jaye ga ke har terhan ki tareef khuda hi ko sazawar hai jo saaray Jahan ka maalik hai
40,1,Haa-Meeem
40,2,is kitaab ka utaara jana khuday-e ghalib o daana ki taraf se hai
40,3,jo gunah bakhsnay wala aur tauba qubool karne wala hai aur sakht azaab dainay wala aur sahib karam hai. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi. isi ki taraf phir kar jana hai
40,4,khuda ki aayton mein wohi log jhagarte hain jo kafir hain. to un logon ka shehron mein chalna phirna tumhe dhokay mein nah daal day
40,5,un se pehlay Nooh ki qoum aur un ke baad aur amtoN ne bhi ( payghambaroon ki ) takzieeb ki. aur har aُmt ne apne paighambar ke baray mein yahi qasadkiya ke is ko pakar len aur behooda ( sh_hbat se ) jhagarte rahay ke is se haq ko zael kar dein to mein ne un ko pakar liya ( so dekh lau ) mera azaab kaisa howa
40,6,aur isi terhan kafiroon ke baray mein bhi tumahray perwar-digaar ki baat poori hochuki hai ke woh ahal dozakh hain
40,7,jo log arsh ko uthaye hue aur jo is ke gurda gird ( halqa bandhay hue ) hain ( yani farishtay ) woh apne perwar-digaar ki tareef ke sath tasbeeh karte rehtay hain aur mominoun ke liye bakhshish mangte rehtay hain. ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar teri rehmat aur tera ilm har cheez ko ihata kiye hue hai to jin logon ne tauba ki aur tairay raste par chalay un ko bakhash day aur dozakh ke azaab se bchale
